member.summary:
Gets or sets a value indicating whether the search should return members that are admins;
true returns only admins, false returns only entities that are not admins and null ignores the IsAdmin property.
Default is null.

Gets or sets a value indicating whether the search should return trashed entities;
true returns only trashed entities, false returns only entities that has not been trashed and null ignores the IsTrashed property.
Default is false.

Gets or sets a value indicating whether the search should return active users;
true returns only active users, false returns only users that are away and null ignores the Active property.
Default is null.

Gets or sets a value indicating whether the result should return built-in users;
true returns only built-in users, false returns only users that are not built-in, and null returns all users. 
Default is false.
